---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Legal Disclaimer | TakeHomePay.nz"
  description="Legal disclaimer for the TakeHomePay.nz New Zealand salary calculator. Important information about the use of this tool."
  canonical="/legal/"
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-light py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Legal Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/90">Important information about using this calculator.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg max-w-none">

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">General Information</h2>
      <p>The information provided by TakeHomePay.nz ("the Website") is for general informational and educational purposes only. All calculations, figures, and information on this website are provided on an "as is" basis without any warranties of any kind, whether express or implied.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Not Professional Advice</h2>
      <p>The salary calculations and tax information provided on this website do not constitute professional tax, financial, legal, or accounting advice. The results produced by our calculator are estimates based on the standard New Zealand PAYE tax system for the 2025-2026 tax year and may not reflect your individual tax situation. You should not rely solely on this calculator for making financial decisions.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Accuracy</h2>
      <p>While we strive to keep the information on this website accurate and up to date with current New Zealand Inland Revenue (IRD) published rates, we make no representations or warranties about the completeness, accuracy, reliability, suitability, or availability of the information, calculations, or results. Any reliance you place on such information is strictly at your own risk.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Limitations</h2>
      <p>This calculator is designed for standard PAYE employment situations. It does not account for:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Multiple sources of income or secondary employment tax codes</li>
        <li>Self-employment, contractor, or sole trader income</li>
        <li>Investment income, rental income, or overseas income</li>
        <li>Working for Families tax credits (detailed calculations)</li>
        <li>Other tax credits, rebates, or exemptions</li>
        <li>Changes in tax rates that may occur during the tax year</li>
        <li>Individual circumstances that may affect tax obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>In no event shall TakeHomePay.nz, its owners, operators, or contributors be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of or in connection with your use of or inability to use this website or its calculations, even if advised of the possibility of such damages.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Professional Advice</h2>
      <p>For accurate, personalised tax advice tailored to your specific circumstances, we strongly recommend consulting with a qualified New Zealand tax advisor, chartered accountant, or contacting Inland Revenue (IRD) directly. The official IRD website at <a href="https://www.ird.govt.nz/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">www.ird.govt.nz</a> provides the most authoritative and current information on New Zealand tax obligations.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">External Links</h2>
      <p>This website may contain links to external websites that are not operated by us. We have no control over the content and practices of these sites and cannot accept responsibility for their respective privacy policies or content.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify this disclaimer at any time without prior notice. By continuing to use the website after any such changes, you acknowledge and agree to the updated disclaimer.</p>

      <p class="text-text-muted mt-8"><em>Last updated: July 2025</em></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
